headline: EA SPORTS FC™ Reveals Star-Studded FC 26 Soundtrack, Featuring First-Ever Professional Footballer on an FC Soundtrack
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., September 15, 2025--Today, Electronic Arts Inc. (NASDAQ: EA) unveiled the highly anticipated soundtrack for EA SPORTS FC™ 26, continuing the franchise’s 20+ year legacy of influencing the global music landscape.
